transcript:
[Ringing]
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello.
Executive: Haan sir call kiya tha aapne?
Customer: Nahi nahi is number se nahi hai kaun number se kiya hua hai.
Executive: Ah acha ye kisi ka number hai 180 wala.
Customer: Haan 180 wala usse kiya.
Executive: Aap kiska number hai sir ye?
Customer: Ye mera naam Aditya hua.
Executive: Inka ye kiska number hai 180 wala is number se.
Customer: Ho sakta hai sir.
Executive: To sir ne call kiya hai kya India Mart ko? Ho sakta hai wahi kiye honge hum to nahi kiye.
Executive: Achcha achcha theek hai theek hai.
Executive: Theek hai thank you.
summary:
